title: That's When (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
That's When is a gem that Taylor kept from us til now! It's her second song with Keith Urban.. How did they end up singing together? And what is this song about? Amy, Nick, Ana and Lacey dissect and discuss.
What did we miss?
